    <releaseNotes>
    - New: Automatic adding: When checking for duplicates is enabled, use the same duplicates found dialog as is used during manual adding.
    - New: ToC Editor: Allow searching to find a location quickly when browsing through the book to select a location for a ToC item
    - New: ToC Editor: Add a button to quickly flatten the entire table of contents
	- New: Conversion: When converting a single book to EPUB or AZW3, add an option to automatically launch the Table of Contents editor after the conversion completes. Found under the Table of Contents section of the conversion dialog.
    - Fixed: calibredb: Nicer error messages when user provides invalid input
    - Fixed: News download: Always use the .jpg extension for jpeg images as apparently Moon+ Reader cannot handle .jpeg
    - Fixed: Fix Book Details popup keyboard navigation doesn't work on a Mac
    - Fixed: Fix a regression that caused the case of the book files to not be changed when changing the case of the title/author on case insensitive filesystems
	- New News Source: Fortune Magazine by Rick Shang
	- New News Source: Eclipse Online by Jim DeVona
    - Improved News Source: RTE news
    - Improved News Source: Various Polish news sources
	- Improved News Source: Psychology Today
	- Improved News Source: Foreign Affairs
	- Improved News Source: History Today
	- Improved News Source: Harpers Magazine (printed edition)
	- Improved News Source: Business Week Magazine
	- Improved News Source: The Hindu
	- Improved News Source: Irish Times
	- Improved News Source: Le Devoir
    </releaseNotes>
